      "content": "hotlines dont fix the money. they dont make the debt go away. i've spent every cent i have and it's just getting worse every single day. it feels like i'm just stuck in this loop where i'm working just to pay for the mess i made, and the mess never gets smaller. i'm just exhausted from fighting something that was never going to end.",
